# Frontend rules

- Preserve existing routing unless the task explicitly asks to change it.
- Do not break API integrations.
- Keep UI state predictable.
- Avoid duplicating API client logic.
- Reuse existing components when possible.
- Improve UX incrementally.
- For checkout, payment, delivery, auth, and seller flows, identify the full user journey before making changes.
- Do not silently change validation behavior.